<br>
What to expect if you join Mayhem's Touch? We want to become a friendly and close guild, that has fun playing together. We won't be having a lot of rules, we just expect you to be loyal and friendly towards other guildies and everybody you play with. Play fair, play nice. We don't try to become as huge as possible, quantity of members is not important to us, quality is tho. <br>
<br>
We are eventually looking for members in the 38+ level range, tho we do accept people from all levels. Why this minimum level? Being part of a guild for us is not just to make fun - except from having a good time we would like to achieve something at the same time. We would like to be able to group up, to organize raids and progress in level together, so we can go and explore new places and keep on going. By having and keeping the members in the same levelrange, you make sure you continue to be able to group up and raid together. <br>
<br>
We expect you to be willing to group up with guildies -how else are you going to get to know eachother and become a close group of friends?. Also we are planning on organizing raids on a 2-weekly base, raids to be organized in weekends. Apart from those raids smaller events can be organized in between, whatever comes to mind can be discussed. You are not obliged to participate in all the organized events, but we do count on you when we plan raids, so you are expected to be there as often as possible. To be able to organize raids to explore new zones, to enable people to finish certain quests or to get a certain item.. we need to be able to count on your participation.<br>
<br>
If you are interested in joining our guild, please leave a message in the Open Membership section.<br>
<br>
We are very excited in getting our new guild together and look forward to the real kick-off. Let's make a strong guild!<br>
<br>
~Vuurvink Tijgeroog &amp; Trungian Terrorstorm<br>
